<br>
It mentioned a particular thing about Sense Heading. At the time I didn't pay a lot of attention since my character is maxxed on that skill. It mentioned doing something that allowed you to invoke sense heading as you used the arrow keys to turn you character. Now I wish I paid attention on how to do that since it would come in handy for my alt character.<br>
<br>
Then I was talking to a friend today that said there was a way to map the 5 key on the keypad that centers your view to also be designated as "use".<br>
<br>
Does anyone know how to do this?<br>
